---
import ArrowDownIcon from './icons/ArrowDown.astro';
import PriceReceipt from './icons/PriceReceipt.astro';
import UserCheck from './icons/UserCheck.astro';
import QuestionMark from './icons/QuestionMark.jsx';
import MagnifyingGlass from './icons/MagnifyingGlass.astro';
---
<section id="how-it-works" class="py-20 px-6 text-base-content text-center">
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
		<h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold ">How It Works</h2>
		<h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-12">4 Easy Steps</h3>
		<div class="grid gap-0 text-left">
			<div class="card bg-base-200 border-1 border-base-300 p-6">
				<h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Step 1</h4>
				<h5 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Tell Us About Your Setup</h5>
				<p class="mb-2">Answer simple questions about your current water heater and hot water needs.</p>
                <p>We don’t store your answers — it’s just to help guide your match.</p>
			</div>
            <ArrowDownIcon class="h-8 w-full text-primary -mt-1 mb-2" />
			<div class="card bg-base-200 border-1 border-base-300 p-6">
				<h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Step 2</h4>
				<h5 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Get A Fixed Price Range For A Replacement</h5>
				<p>We’ll recommend the best-fit model for your home — along with a fixed price range (like $1,475–$1,900) so you know exactly what to expect.</p>
			</div>
            <ArrowDownIcon class="h-8 w-full text-primary -mt-1 mb-2" />
			<div class="card bg-base-200 border-1 border-base-300 p-6">
                <h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Step 3</h4>
                <h5 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Book A Quick-Price-Check To Confirm Your Setup
				</h5>
				<p class=" mb-2">
					You’ve already got your min and max quote. To guarantee your lowest possible price, a tech just needs to quickly check a few key details — venting, gas, water, electrical, drainage, and more.
				</p>
				<p class="mb-2">
					A <span class="font-bold">Quick-Price-Check</span> is exactly that: a technician stops by, checks your home’s setup and final price, and that’s it.

				</p>
				<p class="mb-2">
					No pressure. No upsells. No long-winded presentations. Just a locked-in price and clear answers to your questions.
				</p>
				<p class="mb-2">
					<span class="font-semibold">Bonus</span>: If you’re ready — and there’s time in the schedule — your tech can even get the process started on the spot. That means draining the tank, disconnecting lines, and streamlining your install to save time.
				</p>

				<p class="flex text-bottom items-baseline underline  gap-0 text-primary font-bold cursor-pointer" onclick="document.getElementById('price-lock-modal').classList.add('modal-open')">
					<QuestionMark className="mr-1 mb-auto" />
					Learn More About Our Quick-Price-Check
				</p>
			</div>
            <ArrowDownIcon class="h-8 w-full text-primary -mt-1 mb-2" />
			<div class="card bg-base-200 border-1 border-base-300 p-6">
				<h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Step 4</h4>
				<h5 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Book Your Water Heater Replacement</h5>
				<p class="mb-2">Book online or give us a call — most installs happen the next day.</p>
                <p>
					If you skipped the Quick-Price-Check, we’ll confirm the exact price on-site before we begin.
				</p>

			</div>
            <ArrowDownIcon class="h-8 w-full animate-bounce text-secondary mt-2" />
		</div>
            <a href="/instant-quote/" class="btn btn-secondary text-lg w-full max-w-xs py-2 mx-auto">
                <PriceReceipt />
                <p class="">Get My Instant Quote</p>
            </a>
	</div>

	<!-- create a modal to explain what the Quick Home Check is. it should appear when the highlighted text 'Quick Home Check' in Step 3 is clicked -->
	<div class="modal h-screen px-2 py-4 flex flex-col justify-center items-center" id="price-lock-modal">
			<div class="modal-box shadow-lg text-left sm:text-justify">
				<h3 class="font-bold text-lg">What’s a Quick-Price-Check?</h3>
				<p class="pt-4">Our Instant Quote Tool gives you a solid price range based on typical setups — but not everyone needs the same parts or upgrades.</p>
				<p class="pt-4">Our Instant Quote Tool offers a solid price range based on typical setups, but not everyone needs the same parts or upgrades.</p>
				<p class="pt-4">At your home, we’ll <span class="font-semibold">walk through an Instant Quote together</span> — right from our website — to confirm your answers and make sure the price range makes sense.</p>
				<p class="pt-4">Then we check the unique needs of your water heating system — things like venting, gas line size, or drainage — to see if any specific parts or upgrades are actually required.</p>
				<p class="pt-4">That way, you’ll see exactly how the final price is calculated — <span class="font-semibold">starting with the same Instant Quote everyone gets</span> and adjusted only when your actual setup calls for it.</p>
				<p class="pt-4 font-semibold">Our goal is transparent pricing.</p>
				<p class="font-extrabold text-left pt-4">During the visit we'll:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc text-left pl-6 mb-4 font-bold">
					<li>Walk through your Instant Quote to verify an accurate starting price range</li>
					<li>Make sure you’re not paying for anything unnecessary</li>
					<li>Confirm you get the right parts and equipment</li>
					<li>Ensure your install will be fully up to code</li>
					<li>Answer any questions — from a tech who knows what to look for</li>
					<li>Lock in your final installation price</li>
					<li>Optional:</li>
						<ul class="list-disc text-left pl-6 mb-4 font-bold">
							<li>Book your install appointment, or</li>
							<li>If you’re ready — and we’ve got room in the schedule — your tech can start removing your old water heater on the spot</li>
						</ul>
				</ul>
				<div class="text-gray-500">
				<p class="mb-2">We’ve built a modular pricing system from hundreds of installs, covering nearly every add-on — like chimney liners, gas line upgrades, expansion tank swaps, or relocation work.</p>
				<p class="mb-2">Each add-on has a set price range based on real-world factors like time, distance, or materials — and is determined by a checklist, not “sales instinct.” That means two homes with the same setup always get the same fair price.</p>
				<p class="mb-2">No guesswork. No kidding.</p>
				<p class="mb-2 font-bold">In the time it took to read this, your tech could have already locked in your price. :)</p>
				</div>
				<div class="modal-action">
					<button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="document.getElementById('price-lock-modal').classList.remove('modal-open')">Got it!</button>
			</div>
	</div>
</section>